Dependencies : 
1. opengl
2. glfw
3. Opengl Soil Library : To install run "sudo apt-get install libsoil-dev"


Link to the html page of the assignment : http://www.cse.iitb.ac.in/~anuragshirolkar/cs475/asgn2.3
