Previous versions of youtubr video : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U52283hqNVs

1. To compile just type "make" on the command line.
2. Pressing ESC will quit the program.
3. This code uses OpenGL 2.1.


===================
The Key Mappings
===================

Env Keys:

    Key           |  Usage
    --------------+--------------------------------------------------------
    UP arraow     |  Accelerates the car front 
    Down arrow    |  Deaccelerates the car backward
    Left arrow    |  Turn to left
    Right arrow   |  Turn to right
    key l         |  Switch between two directional lights (Daylight / NightLiht)
    key h         |  Toggle the headlight of car (Use it in night. Turn it off gor energy saving in daytime)
    key c         |  Change Camera Mode (there are 4 camera modes)
    key b         |  Power brake (stops car instantly)
    Enter         |  Transform to flying robo
    Escape        |  Terminate the Program
	key 1         |  change y coordinate of model
	key 2         |  change angle of camera
	key 3         |  change upper arm state left
	key 4         |  change upper arm state right
	key 5         |  change lower arm state left
	key 6         |  change lower arm state right
	key 7         |  change left thigh state
	key 8         |  change right thigh state
	key 9         |  change left knee state
	key 0         |  change right knee state
	key q         |  change camera distance from model
	key w         |  rotate model along x axis
	key e         |  change camera height
	key r         |  rotate model along z axis
	key p         |  toggle sign of value change done with above key presses
	key j         |  store a key frame
	key k         |  toggle recording mode





